===Etymology===
Anglo-Norman, from Old Northern French ''[[wage]]'', a northern variant of Old French ''[[gauge]]'', [[gage]], from Old Franconian ''*waddi'' (cognate with Old English ''[[wedd]]''), from Germanic ''*wadja''.

